{"tid":1613822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"it界毒瘤: 新蒲崗startup - Tofugear Limited","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T04:49:59.000Z","uid":328705,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"340f9b65d3f96591867e5364b6e87ab71f63b024","tid":1613822,"uid":328705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:40:48.000Z","msg":"撻你全朵 咬我食阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2019/9/30 (MON) </strong>去見工<br />\nhr臭雞好撚寸 仲有個牙叔一樣咁寸<br />\n其他公司interview都係齋up<br />\n佢話要我帶埋project去demo<br />\n又話我冇準備 寸我唔怪得搵唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住話想請有heart 冇heart周街有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我開價15k dkgh 15k想點撚樣阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n態度又西 仲話我去見工係求佢請我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想賤價請乜都識咪直接講lo 又要扮請有heart<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後send email吊7佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2019/10/2 (WED)</strong> send左幾封email又唔覆 打電話又冇人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後打通左 原來佢係mon po狗 佢叫我收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我根本無諗過搞你 Tofugear Limited <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次好彩係我 心智堅定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係其他心靈弱小嘅人 可能會被寸到自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以為咗拯救心靈弱小嘅仔仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只能夠唱通街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等佢哋唔洗被寸到自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要小心Tofugear Limited 呢間垃圾公司食人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b5e028aa3b59021e1ca84cdb30bd7dd4c3e802","tid":1613822,"uid":328705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前公司同佢地合作過 做出黎嘅嘢同佢哋個名一樣：<br />\n豆腐渣</blockquote>唔好抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間公司咁有heart<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔信會豆腐渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2810e515441919c2a6cee1056ec892f06663daa5","tid":1613822,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"google唔到你呢篇文"},{"pid":"11f482e99cfe08048ce425d31ed855673aab6717","tid":1613822,"uid":328705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2810e515441919c2a6cee1056ec892f06663daa5","tid":1613822,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"google唔到你呢篇文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"唔識點推上google<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c933dad99da2a76c684c1bc1200ed37b8e416913","tid":1613822,"uid":96754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"呢間嘢個founder係咪鬼佬？"},{"pid":"3d44c4bcc04f976a38023f6b9b1133a5d09ee454","tid":1613822,"uid":328705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:47:24.000Z","msg":"好有heart嘅管理層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sc00Xac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSc00Xac.png&h=438c6d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvEXZoz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvEXZoz.png&h=5fde75b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjjJavh.png\" data-thumbna